{"tid":1022704,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"恐怖「幽靈斷腳」！加拿大海岸又發現穿NIKE鞋斷腳　12年來第15起","createTime":"2019-02-15T08:00:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-15T08:48:58.000Z","uid":212399,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"ffb906698834c8f13df7c8c581148684fba71542","tid":1022704,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T08:00:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3897/d3897862.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3897%2Fd3897862.jpg&h=96c1595a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲加拿大卑詩省已發現15隻人類斷腳飄在海岸上。（圖／取自卑詩省政府官網）<br />\n國際中心／綜合報導<br />\n加拿大卑詩省沿岸（British Columbia）自2007年以來，已陸續發現多隻人類「斷腳」漂浮在海岸。當局11日又公布一起最新斷腳事件，也是「幽靈腳事件」的第15起。最新的幽靈腳被發現時還穿著NIKE的球鞋，經調查後推測，應是年齡小於50歲男子的斷腳，不過目前尚未找到符合的DNA配對。<br />\n綜合外媒報導，這起最新「幽靈腳事件」是去年9月在溫哥華發現的，近日政府才公布出來。這隻斷腳被發現時還穿著NIKE淺灰色「Nike Free RN」款式，襪子則為藍色的，大小為美國尺碼9.5，而這雙鞋約在2017年2月1日至4月17日間製造，因此被發現時鞋子看起來還很新。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3897/d3897861.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3897%2Fd3897861.jpg&h=184e5eb9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲依骨骼結構推測為50歲以下男性。（圖／取自卑詩省政府官網）<br />\n當地法醫中心指出，依據這隻斷腳的骨骼結構判斷，主人年齡大約是50歲以下，且性別為男性，但檢驗DNA後還未找到符合的匹配對象。這是自2007年8月以來，加拿大卑詩省海岸上發現的第15隻人腳。<br />\n據卑詩省當局表示，在這15起「幽靈腳」事件中，有10人能與失踪人口配對，但其中5隻腳仍然身份不明。 報導指出，幽靈腳事件已引發全世界的猜測，有些人認為是2004年海嘯等自然災害造成，而另一部分的人則認為與連環殺手或犯罪組織有關。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190215/1378808.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20190215%2F1378808.htm&d=rje4l1xmTn6y9o%2BHBfPafzIStCm0mHK7%2Bbmf%2BnNiY0c%3D&h=99c7d060\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190215/1378808.htm</a>"},{"pid":"98d243fe7ddf990515bc1bc6b28190a448b46b07","tid":1022704,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T08:03:36.000Z","msg":"血色除夕夜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7f6856180b761dcfe019802f8d95f7cde3f40c2","tid":1022704,"uid":35014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T08:05:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0bb431f94e3ca6677b5b1ee0312925708320f0fc","tid":1022704,"uid":95,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T08:05:21.000Z","msg":"邪教或連環殺手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8411a4e37a25a7248640fd6c250f1d26837e6d4b","tid":1022704,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0bb431f94e3ca6677b5b1ee0312925708320f0fc","tid":1022704,"uid":95,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T08:05:21.000Z","msg":"邪教或連環殺手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T08:10:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64fd701a4fc81755160dc5930c82b313cd7b4d2b","tid":1022704,"uid":14073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T08:13:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fDq7wFS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfDq7wFS.png&h=fd020029&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d4a1075fde8d767fa80745f23efacabebec0182a","tid":1022704,"uid":19289,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T08:21:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AWFaj4IQ4ro#t=2m43s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DAWFaj4IQ4ro%23t%3D2m43s&d=rje4l1xmTn6y9o%2BHBfPafzIStCm0mHK7%2Bbmf%2BnNiY0c%3D&h=aa1f210a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AWFaj4IQ4ro#t=2m43s</a>"},{"pid":"eddd83e2dc8aaff7cdafe1b2078cc5bc0b1fb88d","tid":1022704,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T08:22:52.000Z","msg":"呢單有無紀錄片講過"},{"pid":"c9bed6704f3c0a9033bb2666afad8d3ffc6f8bf6","tid":1022704,"uid":34186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T08:25:25.000Z","msg":"自然災害點整到咁多斷腳出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 似連環殺手"},{"pid":"c3e519577648615a7945079e24ed077c146ec6dc","tid":1022704,"uid":72749,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T08:25:45.000Z","msg":"有冇可能係墨西哥黑幫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢地好鐘意分屍"},{"pid":"2dc7fa3f0ab6a33036015ad33dd6694db3563e4b","tid":1022704,"uid":24615,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T08:33:00.000Z","msg":"其實D斷腳有鞋有晒生產批次code紀錄 <br />\n要查D鞋大約幾時係邊出售好易<br />\n<br />\n最少都鎖定到係邊個國家/州份,係唔係自然災害定人為一目了然"},{"pid":"05c3523358c0a7d84e445e6665f42a614dc62040","tid":1022704,"uid":220331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"64fd701a4fc81755160dc5930c82b313cd7b4d2b","tid":1022704,"uid":14073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T08:13:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fDq7wFS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfDq7wFS.png&h=fd020029&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T08:44:22.000Z","msg":"係咩標誌嚟？"},{"pid":"d65e204aab46d30573bdf8caf482d7a869e91776","tid":1022704,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2dc7fa3f0ab6a33036015ad33dd6694db3563e4b","tid":1022704,"uid":24615,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T08:33:00.000Z","msg":"其實D斷腳有鞋有晒生產批次code紀錄 <br />\n要查D鞋大約幾時係邊出售好易<br />\n<br />\n最少都鎖定到係邊個國家/州份,係唔係自然災害定人為一目了然"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T08:45:01.000Z","msg":"上面咪有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2017-4-17<br />\n<br />\n最近的"},{"pid":"24abfc12d2418d6151604bf85393afc8ff95777b","tid":1022704,"uid":80814,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T08:48:58.000Z","msg":"聽過話可能係跳海自殺或意外落水遇溺死亡嘅屍身甩落出嚟，因為其他完整屍身都被海嘅微生物同細菌分解，得返有著鞋嘅腳掌可以保護到，但都會腐爛嚴重驗唔到係死者身份。至於點解成日沖去嗰度，就係同水流有關。<br />\n<br />\n不過跳海自殺或遇溺嘅人有咁多係著住鞋？似係完整屍身掉落海？"}]}